            <ul>
                <li>Exploring new technologies and frameworks</li>
                <li>Contributing to open-source projects</li>
                <li>Reading tech blogs and staying updated on industry trends</li>
                <li>Attending hackathons and coding competitions</li>
                <li>Enjoying outdoor activities like hiking and photography</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <p>Connect with me on <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/your-linkedin-profile" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a></p>
